<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>오류가 발생했습니다 - ExcelApp</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      
      .error-container {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 40px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        max-width: 500px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      
      .error-icon {
        font-size: 64px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        color: #e74c3c;
      }
      
      h1 {
        color: #2c3e50;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      
      p {
        color: #7f8c8d;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      
      .btn {
        background: #3498db;
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: inline-block;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: background 0.3s;
      }
      
      .btn:hover {
        background: #2980b9;
      }
      
      .error-id {
        background: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 8px 16px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
        margin-top: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="error-container">
      <div class="error-icon">⚠️</div>
      <h1>오류가 발생했습니다</h1>
      <p>
        요청을 처리하는 중에 문제가 발생했습니다.<br>
        잠시 후 다시 시도해주세요.
      </p>
      
      <%= link_to '홈으로 돌아가기', root_path, class: 'btn' %>
      
      <% if Current.request_id %>
        <div class="error-id">
          오류 ID: <%= Current.request_id %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>